Get closest colour name from rgb in #RStats
rgb2col <- function(x){ # x is rgb vector length 3
rc <- colors()
rs <- t(col2rgb(rc))
d <- as.matrix(dist(rbind(x,rs),diag=T,upper=T))
y <- rs[which.min(d[2:nrow(d)])]
names(y) <- paste("dist", round(min(d[2:nrow(d)]), 1))
return(y)
} https://t.co/mzMT3k4fB3
